attributes.mlflow.spanInputs:
{"database_schema": ""Description for table: CreatorContract"
type CreatorContract @entity {
  "Unique identifier for the creator contract."
  id: ID!
  "Block number in which the contract was created."
  blockNumber: BigInt!
  "Timestamp of the block when the contract was created."
  timestamp: BigInt!
  "Hash of the transaction that created the contract."
  transactionHash: Bytes!
  "Index of the transaction within the block."
  transactionIndex: BigInt!
  "Index of the log entry within the transaction."
  logIndex: BigInt!
  "Address associated with the event."
  eventAddress: Bytes!
  "Address from which the transaction was sent."
  eventTxFrom: Bytes!
  "Address to which the transaction was sent, if applicable."
  eventTxTo: Bytes
  "Address of the contract implementation."
  implementation: Bytes!
  "Address of the deployer of the contract."
  deployer: Bytes!
  "Address of the creator of the contract."
  creator: Bytes!
  "Indicates whether the contract is paused."
  paused: Boolean!
  "Address of the owner of the contract."
  owner: Bytes!
  "Percentage of secondary royalties."
  secondaryRoyaltyPercentage: BigInt!
  "Address of the minter."
  minter: Bytes!
  "Default handler for funds."
  defaultFundsHandler: Bytes!
  "List of default recipients for funds."
  defaultFundsRecipients: [Bytes!]!
  "List of shares for each default fund recipient."
  defaultFundsShares: [BigInt!]!
  "ERC165 interface ID, if applicable."
  ERC165InterfaceID: Bytes
  "Indicates if batch buy-it-now is enabled."
  isBatchBuyItNow: Boolean!
  "Indicates if the contract is hidden."
  isHidden: Boolean!
  "State of the transfer process."
  transferState: BigInt!
  "Total number of editions available."
  totalNumOfEditions: BigInt!
  "Total number of tokens sold."
  totalNumOfTokensSold: BigInt!
  "Total Ethereum value of sales."
  totalEthValueOfSales: BigDecimal!
  "Total number of transfers made."
  totalNumOfTransfers: BigInt!
  "List of editions associated with the contract."
  editions: [Edition!]!
  "Name of the contract."
  name: String
  "Symbol representing the contract."
  symbol: String
  "Registry for filtering purposes."
  filterRegistry: Bytes
}"}
